The '''1897 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their seventh ever season of organized football. The Keydets went 3-2 under first year head coach [[R. N. Groner]].<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
